####################################################
1) Required Libraries

$ apt-get install libboost-all-dev libboost-dev

####################################################
2) Compiling Binaries

$ make all

####################################################
3) Run Binaries

The make file creates two binaries. The OpenMSC and a receiver dummy. If both binaries are located on the same machine just invoke:

$ ./receiverDummy 8000

in one terminal and 

$ ./openmsc -i 127.0.0.1 -p 8000

in another one.
